Nomad's chronicles - part 2
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Every intelligent species strives for knowledge.
Discovering truth is accepted as honorable and useful.
So thought our people until we found the monolith.


We know nothing about the builders of this strange and alien structure.
Other than all previously found ruins of fallen civilizations, it was built with technologies surpassing our own.


And its shape, simple as it might have been, was... inspiring.